		format slot 9 of player with black stained glass pane with name "&0." to be unstealable
		format slot 10 of player with leather chestplate coloured red with name "&4Flame Armour" with lore "&7Mythical Armour obtained by||&7Only the greatest adventurers!" to close then run [make player execute command "cg cgbuyFlame"]
		format slot 11 of player with black stained glass pane with name "&0." to be unstealable
		format slot 12 of player with leather chestplate coloured black with name "&7Cursed Armour" with lore "&7Mythical Armour obtained by||&7Only the greatest adventurers!" to close then run [make player execute command "cg cgbuycursed"]
