		format slot 14 of player with leather chestplate coloured blue with name "&3Mytheral Armour" with lore "&7Mythical Armour obtained by||&7Only the greatest adventurers!" to close then run [make player execute command "cg cgbuymytheral"]
		format slot 15 of player with black stained glass pane with name "&0." to be unstealable
		format slot 16 of player with leather chestplate coloured green with name "&3Vermit" with lore "&7Mythical Armour obtained by||&7Only the greatest adventurers!" to close then run [make player execute command "cg cgbuyvermit"]
